Interface CatalogObjectImpl.ArrayAdapters

Enclosing class:
CatalogObjectImpl
public static interface CatalogObjectImpl.ArrayAdapters
Instances of ArrayAdapter for types used in the catalogs.

A holder interface so these won't be instantiated unless wanted.

    • RELOPTIONS_INSTANCE

      static final ArrayAdapter<Map<Lexicals.Identifier.Simple,String>> RELOPTIONS_INSTANCE
      Map<Identifier.Simple,String> from an array of TEXT that represents 'reloptions' (as used on relations, attributes, and foreign wrappers / servers / tables, at least).

      The String value is never expected to be null (PostgreSQL's transformRelOptions will have substituted true where an option with no value was parsed), and this adapter will assume the first '=' in each element delimits the key from the value (that is, that no key can be an SQL delimited identifier containing '=', though PostgreSQL as of 17 does not enforce that).
